code: // ------------------------------------------------------------------------ // Accumulator // ------------------------------------------------------------------------ /**  * Consider using {@link #add(long)} instead for primitive long values  */ @Override public void add(Long value) {     this.min = Math.min(this.min, value). }
@Override public void merge(Accumulator<Long, Long> other) {     this.min = Math.min(this.min, other.getLocalValue()). }
@Override public LongMinimum clone() {     LongMinimum clone = new LongMinimum().     clone.min = this.min.     return clone. }
